query: relation extraction, contrastive learning, pre trained language models, erica
sql:
SELECT
  p.paper_id,
  p.title,
  p.abstract,
  p.venue,
  p.year,
  p.citation_count
FROM Papers p
LEFT JOIN PaperAuthors pa ON p.paper_id = pa.paper_id
LEFT JOIN Authors a ON pa.author_id = a.author_id
WHERE
  (
    (p.title ILIKE '%relation extraction%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%relation extraction%')
    OR (p.title ILIKE '%contrastive learning%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%contrastive learning%')
    OR (p.title ILIKE '%pre trained language model%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%pre trained language model%' OR
        p.title ILIKE '%pre-trained language model%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%pre-trained language model%')
    OR (p.title ILIKE '%erica%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%erica%')
  )
ORDER BY
  CASE
    WHEN p.title ILIKE '%relation extraction%' THEN 4 ELSE 0 END +
  CASE
    WHEN p.abstract ILIKE '%relation extraction%' THEN 3 ELSE 0 END +
  CASE
    WHEN p.title ILIKE '%contrastive learning%' THEN 4 ELSE 0 END +
  CASE
    WHEN p.abstract ILIKE '%contrastive learning%' THEN 3 ELSE 0 END +
  CASE
    WHEN p.title ILIKE '%pre trained language model%' OR p.title ILIKE '%pre-trained language model%' THEN 3 ELSE 0 END +
  CASE
    WHEN p.abstract ILIKE '%pre trained language model%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%pre-trained language model%' THEN 2 ELSE 0 END +
  CASE
    WHEN p.title ILIKE '%erica%' THEN 2 ELSE 0 END +
  CASE
    WHEN p.abstract ILIKE '%erica%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
DESC,
  p.citation_count DESC NULLS LAST,
  p.year DESC NULLS LAST
LIMIT 100
